{"id":"FAXI05","scripts":[{"stopbgm":true,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"ってことは、オレたちはあのヴェネトに対抗するため、人類に作られたってことか？","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":1,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"そうですね。結果的に言うとそうなりました。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"なら、オレたちは所詮人を殺めるための兵器だな。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":1,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"そうではありません。どの時代でも人間は信仰と英雄を必要とします。信仰と英雄なくして人間は生き延びられません。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"つまり、オレたちは彼らにとっての英雄ってことか？","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":1,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"今はまだそうではありませんよ。あなたが動けるようになるまでは……ふふっ。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"リシュリュー姉！またオレのことを馬鹿にしやがって！あと少しだ、あともう少しであんたを追い越してやるからな！","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":1,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"そうですね。待っていますよ。そういえば、私たちの「名前」の意味……知っていますか？","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"名前？","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":1,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"「船」である私たちの「名前」は人類の偉人から預かった、大いなる期待を込められたもの…","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"ふーん、オレの「名前」はなんなのさ？","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":1,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"私掠船……つまり海賊ですね…ある意味似合っていませんか？","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"はあ！？また馬鹿にしたな！三度目はないからな！","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":1,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"はいはい。ですが…国土を守る栄光ある英雄になるか、ただただ死をもたらす兵器になるか、今度は本人次第――私たち自身が決めることです。","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":0,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"…………","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"blackBg":true,"side":1,"dir":1,"actorName":"???","say":"くれぐれもその「名前」に恥じる選択をしないように――","typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"flashin":{"alpha":[1,0],"delay":1,"black":true,"dur":1},"bgName":"bg_story_faxi2","dir":1,"withoutPainting":true,"say":"…またこの夢か。まったく笑えない冗談だな。","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"flashout":{"alpha":[0,1],"black":true,"dur":1},"actor":905010,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"大洋最強の戦艦にして、堂々たる騎士様が、今やよそ者の力にすがるというこの有様だ。ふん。","bgName":"bg_story_faxi2","side":2,"dir":1,"withoutPainting":true,"actor":905010,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}},{"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"――不甲斐ないにもほどがあるぞ。この馬鹿姉が。","bgName":"bg_story_faxi2","side":2,"dir":1,"withoutPainting":true,"actor":905010,"typewriter":{"speed":0.05,"speedUp":0.01}}],"fadeOut":0.5,"fadeType":1,"occlusion":2,"mode":2,"once":true}